@startuml Vehicle_Ownership_Transfer
title Vehicle Ownership Transfer - Failure Paths

autonumber
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20

actor "New User" as User
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "Enrollment Service" as Cloud
participant "Vehicle (TCU)" as Car

== Failure Path A: Incorrect Pairing Code ==
User -> App : Enters '999999' (Wrong Code)
App -> Cloud : POST /verify-transfer (VIN, '999999')
Cloud -> Cloud : Validate Code Match
Cloud --> App : 401 Unauthorized: 'Invalid Code'
App -> User : "Code does not match. Please try again (2 attempts left)."

== Failure Path B: Vehicle Offline (Timeout) ==
User -> App : Requests Pairing Code
App -> Cloud : POST /initiate-transfer (VIN)
Cloud -> Car : MQTT: DisplayPairingCode ('123456')
... Wait 30 Seconds (Timeout) ...
Car --[#red]> Cloud : [No Acknowledgment / Offline]
Cloud --> App : 504 Gateway Timeout: 'Vehicle Unreachable'
App -> User : "We can't reach your car. Ensure it is parked in an area with cellular signal."

== Failure Path C: Security Lockout ==
User -> App : Enters Wrong Code (3rd Time)
App -> Cloud : POST /verify-transfer (VIN, 'wrong_code')
Cloud -> Cloud : Exceeds Max Retries
Cloud --> App : 403 Forbidden: 'Lockout'
App -> User : "Too many attempts. Please contact Support or wait 24 hours."

@endum